videos.description: Carsen Edwards knocks down a contested 3-pointer to become the schools all-time leader in 3-pointers made.
videos.headline: Edwards drains historic 3-pointer

videos.description: Purdue forward Matt Haarms gets a layup while getting hacked on the way up.
videos.headline: Haarms goes up strong with the foul

videos.description: Northwestern guard Anthony Gaines finds A.J. Turner in the corner for three to pull within 7.
videos.headline: Turner's 3-pointer cuts into deficit

videos.description: Carsen Edwards dials one up from long distance to give Purdue an 11-point lead.
videos.headline: Edwards knocks down triple to extend Purdue's lead
